\id 2TH - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020
\h 2 Jo-Thesalonika
\toc1 Jo-Thesalonika Mar Ariyo
\toc2 2 Jo-Thesalonika
\toc3 2Thes
\mt1 2 Jo-Thesalonika
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 An Paulo gi Sila kod Timotheo,
\b
\p Wandikonu un kanisa mar jo-Thesalonika, man kuom Nyasaye Wuonwa kod Ruoth Yesu Kristo:
\b
\p 
\v 2 Ngʼwono gi kwe moa kuom Nyasaye Wuoro kod Ruoth Yesu Kristo obed kodu.
\b
\s1 Lemo kod dwoko erokamano
\p 
\v 3 Nyaka wadwokne Nyasaye erokamano kinde duto nikech un jowetewa kendo owinjore watim kamano nikech yie ma un-go medo bedo motegno, kendo hera muherorugo ngʼato gi ngʼato bende medore.
\v 4 Kuom mano, wasebedo ka wapwoyou e kind kanisa Nyasaye, kawanyisogi kuom kindau kod yieu motegno momiyo udhil e dier sand kod tem duto muyudo.
\p 
\v 5 Magi duto nyiso ni buch Nyasaye nikare, nikech bangʼ neno sand kod tem to e giko nokwanu kaka joma owinjore yudo gweth mar pinyruoth Nyasaye.
\v 6 Nyasaye en ngʼama kare omiyo obiro kumo joma sandou,
\v 7 to un muyudo sand obiro miyou yweyo, kaachiel kodwa. Mano notimre chiengʼ ma Ruoth Yesu nofwenyre e mach makakni kolor oa e polo, kaachiel gi malaika mage maroteke.
\v 8 Enokum joma okia Nyasaye kendo ma ok orito puonj mar Injili mar Ruodhwa Yesu.
\v 9 Giniyud kum ma en lal manyaka chiengʼ, koriembogi oko e nyim Ruoth Nyasaye kendo mabor gi tekone man-gi duongʼ.
\v 10 En odiechiengʼ ma Ruoth noduogie mondo joge maler omiye duongʼ kendo joma oyie duto omiye luor. Un bende unubed achiel kuom jogo, nikech ne uyie wach mane wakelonu.
\p 
\v 11 Ka un gi gima chalo kama e pachu, to mano emomiyo walamonu kinde duto, mondo omi Nyasachwa okwanu kaka joma owinjore gi luongne, mondo tekone ochop dwaro mabeyo duto ma un-go kod tije duto mutimo nikech yie ma un-go.
\v 12 Walemo ni mondo nying Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo oyud duongʼ kuomu, kendo mondo un bende uyud duongʼ kuome. Mano mondo otimrenu kuom ngʼwono mar Nyasachwa kod Ruoth Yesu Kristo.
\c 2
\s1 Ngʼat mochayo Chik
\p 
\v 1 To koro owetewa, kuom wach biro mar Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo kendo kaka ibiro chokowa kanyakla mondo waromne,
\v 2 wakwayou mondo kik uparru kendo kik chunyu chandre ni weche mokor, kata weche mokelnu, kata baruwa moro miwacho ni oa irwa, mawacho ni odiechiengʼ mar Ruoth osechopo.
\v 3 Kik uyie ngʼato wuondu e yo moro amora, nikech odiechiengʼno ok nobi nyaka ngʼanyo maduongʼ chopi, kendo nyaka ngʼat mochayo chik fwenyre, ma en jal mochanne tho e mach manyaka chiengʼ.
\v 4 Obiro sungore kokwedo gimoro amora miluongo ni Nyasaye kata gimoro amora milamo. Bende nohedhre bet kata ei hekalu mar Nyasaye kolandore owuon ni en Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 5 Donge unyalo paro ni ne anyisou gigi kane an kodu?
\v 6 To koro ungʼeyo gima pod omone fwenyore, ni nyaka obi mana e kinde moketne.
\v 7 Teko mopondo mar tij chayo chik koro osechako tich. To ka jal motamo ngʼat mochayo chik ogol oko, to tekono nofwenyre.
\v 8 Bangʼe jal mochayo chik nofwenyre, to Ruoth Yesu nobi gi duongʼne duto miwuoro, nonege gi muya moa e dhoge kendo notiek tekone duto.
\v 9 Jal mochayo Chikno nobi kaluwore gi dwaro mar Satan ka en gi teko duto mar timo honni gi ranyisi mag miriambo,
\v 10 kokonyore gi kit wuond maricho duto mondo owitgo joma lal. Jogo lal nikech negitamore hero adiera makelo warruok.
\v 11 Kuom mano Nyasaye ooronigi teko maduongʼ marundo pachgi mondo omi giyie gi weche mag miriambo,
\v 12 omiyo Ruoth nongʼad bura ni ji duto motamore yie adiera, ka gihero mana timo timbe maricho.
\s1 Chungʼuru motegno
\p 
\v 13 Owetewa ma Ruoth ohero, onego wadwokne Nyasaye erokamano kinde duto ka waparou nikech Nyasaye noyierou\f + \fr 2:13 \ft Loko moko machon wacho ni, \fqa “Nyasaye noyierou kaka nyak mar olemo mokwongo”.\f* nyaka aa chakruok mondo owaru komiyo ngimau doko maler kuom teko mar Roho Maler kaachiel gi yie muyiego kuom adiera.
\v 14 Mano emomiyo noluongou kane urwako Injili mane wayalonu mondo un bende uyud duongʼ mar Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo.
\p 
\v 15 Kuom mano, jowetewa, chunguru motegno, kendo makuru matek puonj mane wapuonjou gi dhowa kata gi barupewa.
\p 
\v 16 Mad Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo owuon kod Nyasaye Wuonwa, ma noherowa momiyowa jip mosiko kod geno maber, kuom ngʼwonone,
\v 17 ojiw chunyu kendo omiu teko e yore duto kendo e weche mabeyo.
\c 3
\s1 Paulo okwayo lamo
\p 
\v 1 Mogik, jowetewa, lemnwauru mondo Wach Ruoth Yesu olandre piyo piyo kendo mondo ji omi wachno duongʼ, mana kaka notimore e dieru.
\v 2 Lemnwauru bende mondo Nyasaye oreswa e lwet joma timbegi mono kendo ma joricho, nikech ji duto ok nigi yie motegno.
\v 3 Ruoth en ja-adiera, omiyo obiro miyou teko kendo obiro ritou e lwet Ngʼama Rach.
\v 4 Wan gi chir kuom Ruoth ni utimo gik ma wawacho kendo ni ubiro medo timo kamano.
\v 5 Ruoth mondo omi chunyu omed hero Nyasaye kendo ubed gi kinda machalo mane Kristo ne gigo.
\s1 Siem kuom joma ok dwar tiyo
\p 
\v 6 Wachikou jowetewa e nying Ruoth Yesu Kristo mondo upogru gi jowete ma budho abudha kendo ok lu puonj mane uyudo kuomwa.
\v 7 Nikech un uwegi ungʼeyo ni onego ulu ranyisi mar kit ngimawa. Ne ok wabudh abudha kane wan kodu,
\v 8 kendo kata chiemb ngʼato ne ok wachamo ma ok wachulo. To ne watiyo odiechiengʼ gotieno, ka watiyo gi lwetewa kendo ka watiyo tich matek mondo kik wami ngʼato moro amora kuomu tingʼ mapek.
\v 9 Ne watimo kamano ok nikech ne waonge gi ratiro mar yudo kony moa kuomu, to ne wadwaro mondo wabednu ranyisi maber ma unyalo luwo.
\v 10 Nikech kata e kinde mane wan kodu ne wamiyou chik niya, “Ka ngʼato budho abudha ma ok odwar tiyo to kik ochiem.”
\p 
\v 11 Wawinjo ni jomoko kuomu budho abudha. Ok giti, tije jowetegi ema gikeloe weche manono.
\v 12 E nying Ruoth Yesu Kristo, wachiko kendo wasiemo joma kamago mondo gibed mos kendo giti matek mondo giyud yo ma gikonyorego.
\v 13 To un, jowetena, kik uol gi timo maber.
\p 
\v 14 Ka ngʼato angʼata otamore luwo weche mawandikonu e baruwani to ngʼiuru ngʼatno maber. Kik uriwru kode, mondo eka wiye okuodi kuom timne mobam.
\v 15 Kik ukawe kaka jasigu, to siemeuru asiema kaka owadu kuom Ruoth.
\b
\s1 Mos mogik
\p 
\v 16 Koro Ruodh kwe owuon mondo omiu kwe mare pile e yore duto. Ruoth mondo obed kodu uduto.
\b
\p 
\v 17 An Paulo ema andikonu mosni gi lweta awuon, en kido maketo e barupena duto kendo mano e kaka andiko.
\b
\p 
\v 18 Ngʼwono mar Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo obed kodu un duto.
